@baseUrl = http://localhost:5118

### ============================================================
### Authors
### ============================================================

### List all authors
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/authors?page=1&pageSize=10

### Search authors by name
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/authors?search=Austen

### Get author by ID (Jane Austen)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/authors/1

### Create a new author
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/authors
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "firstName": "George",
  "lastName": "Orwell",
  "biography": "English novelist and essayist, journalist and critic. Best known for Animal Farm and 1984.",
  "birthDate": "1903-06-25",
  "country": "United Kingdom"
}

### Update an author
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/authors/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "firstName": "Jane",
  "lastName": "Austen",
  "biography": "English novelist known for her wit, social commentary, and insight into the lives of early 19th-century British women.",
  "birthDate": "1775-12-16",
  "country": "United Kingdom"
}

### Delete an author (will fail if author has books)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/authors/1

### ============================================================
### Categories
### ============================================================

### List all categories
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/categories?page=1&pageSize=10

### Get category by ID (Fiction)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/categories/1

### Create a new category
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/categories
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Philosophy",
  "description": "Books exploring fundamental questions about existence, knowledge, and ethics"
}

### Update a category
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/categories/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Fiction",
  "description": "Narrative works of imagination, including novels, novellas, and short stories"
}

### Delete a category (will fail if category has books)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/categories/1

### ============================================================
### Books
### ============================================================

### List all books
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/books?page=1&pageSize=10

### Search books by title
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/books?search=Foundation

### Search books by author name
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/books?search=Asimov

### Filter books by availability (available only)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/books?available=true

### Filter books that are unavailable
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/books?available=false

### Sort books by title descending
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/books?sortBy=title&sortDirection=desc

### Get book by ID (Pride and Prejudice)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/books/1

### Create a new book
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/books
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Emma",
  "isbn": "978-0-14-143958-7",
  "publisher": "Penguin Classics",
  "publicationYear": 1815,
  "description": "A comic novel about youthful hubris and romantic misunderstandings.",
  "pageCount": 474,
  "language": "English",
  "totalCopies": 2,
  "authorIds": [1],
  "categoryIds": [1, 6]
}

### Update a book
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/books/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Pride and Prejudice",
  "isbn": "978-0-14-143951-8",
  "publisher": "Penguin Classics",
  "publicationYear": 1813,
  "description": "A romantic novel that also serves as a masterful social commentary on the British landed gentry of the early 19th century.",
  "pageCount": 432,
  "language": "English",
  "totalCopies": 3,
  "authorIds": [1],
  "categoryIds": [1, 6]
}

### Delete a book (will fail if book has active loans)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/books/2

### Get loan history for a book
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/books/1/loans?page=1&pageSize=10

### Get active reservations for a book (I, Robot - has reservations)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/books/4/reservations?page=1&pageSize=10

### ============================================================
### Patrons
### ============================================================

### List all patrons
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/patrons?page=1&pageSize=10

### Search patrons by name
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/patrons?search=Alice

### Filter patrons by membership type
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/patrons?membershipType=Premium

### Get patron by ID (Alice Johnson - has active loans)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/patrons/1

### Create a new patron
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/patrons
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "firstName": "Grace",
  "lastName": "Lee",
  "email": "grace.lee@email.com",
  "phone": "555-0107",
  "address": "111 Willow Way, Springfield",
  "membershipType": "Student"
}

### Update a patron
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/patrons/2
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "firstName": "Bob",
  "lastName": "Williams",
  "email": "bob.williams@email.com",
  "phone": "555-0102",
  "address": "456 Maple Ave, Suite 2, Springfield",
  "membershipType": "Premium"
}

### Deactivate a patron (will fail if patron has active loans)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/patrons/6

### Get patron's loans (Alice - has active and returned loans)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/patrons/1/loans?page=1&pageSize=10

### Get patron's active loans only
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/patrons/1/loans?status=active

### Get patron's reservations
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/patrons/1/reservations?page=1&pageSize=10

### Get patron's fines
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/patrons/4/fines?page=1&pageSize=10

### Get patron's unpaid fines only
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/patrons/4/fines?status=unpaid

### ============================================================
### Loans
### ============================================================

### List all loans
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/loans?page=1&pageSize=10

### Filter loans by status
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/loans?status=active

### Filter overdue loans
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/loans?overdue=true

### Filter loans by date range
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/loans?fromDate=2026-03-01&toDate=2026-03-31

### Get loan by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/loans/1

### Check out a book (create a loan - Sense and Sensibility for Carol)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/loans
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "bookId": 2,
  "patronId": 3
}

### Return a book (loan 2 - Foundation returned by Bob)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/loans/2/return

### Renew a loan (loan 1 - Pride and Prejudice for Alice)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/loans/1/renew

### Get all overdue loans (also flags overdue)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/loans/overdue?page=1&pageSize=10

### --- Business Rule Tests ---

### Attempt checkout for inactive patron (Frank Wilson - patron 6)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/loans
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "bookId": 2,
  "patronId": 6
}

### Attempt to renew an overdue loan (loan 5 - David's overdue loan)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/loans/5/renew

### Attempt checkout when no copies available (I, Robot - 0 available)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/loans
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "bookId": 4,
  "patronId": 5
}

### ============================================================
### Reservations
### ============================================================

### List all reservations
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/reservations?page=1&pageSize=10

### Filter reservations by status
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/reservations?status=pending

### Get reservation by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/reservations/1

### Create a reservation (reserve One Hundred Years of Solitude for Emily)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/reservations
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "bookId": 5,
  "patronId": 5
}

### Attempt to reserve a book patron already has on active loan (Alice has loan for book 1)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/reservations
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "bookId": 1,
  "patronId": 1
}

### Cancel a reservation
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/reservations/2/cancel

### Fulfill a ready reservation (reservation 3 - Foundation for Alice)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/reservations/3/fulfill

### ============================================================
### Fines
### ============================================================

### List all fines
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/fines?page=1&pageSize=10

### Filter fines by status
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/fines?status=unpaid

### Get fine by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/fines/1

### Pay a fine
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/fines/1/pay

### Waive a fine
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/fines/2/waive
